\v 25 âWĂ«Ă«n yokot kaĂ¶ap pi yaak wakaim olĂ«ak kaalak wais kaat temanĂ¶m yewasem kat wiin intĂ¶ ngĂ¶nre tanre pĂ¶t yeĂ«a.
