\v 29 PĂ«l Ă«Ă«n pi kangiir epĂ«l mĂ«Ă«a. âKat wi. Ne krismaki selap pan nim naĂ« pas ya mĂ«neimeĂ« nim ngĂ¶n nent wa noolaan Ă«aut. PĂ«l Ă«Ă«n ni pol meme ru namp nem karurĂ¶aring Ă«rĂ«psawi Ă«Ă«maan nenangkĂ«n Ă«aupĂ¶k
\v 30 nim ru pipmor pi Ă¶ng paspas yaaurĂ¶aan nim omnant pout won wes olĂ«ak kaalak waisĂ«n ni pimĂ«Ă«nĂ¶kĂ«Ă«r purmakaĂ¶ ru ompyaĂ¶ mĂ«sĂ«pringĂ«p yamĂ¶Ă¶n.â
