\v 19 WeĂ«re kosangring wakaim olĂ«ak wĂ«wĂ« kosangĂ«t Ă¶nĂ«Ă«t.â
\s1 Yesuuk Yerusalem kaĂ¶ utpet Ă«Ă«pnaata ngĂ¶nte Ă¶k mĂ«Ă«a
