\v 17 PĂ«l mĂ«ak wain kelĂ¶n nent wak Anutuun yowe mĂ«ak epĂ«l mĂ«Ă«a. âAr epĂ«t wak ngawi neĂ«.
\v 18 Ne niamaan. Yangerak eprek wain iit peene nĂ«Ă«n pet yair. Arring kaalak nanĂ«n wĂ« Ă«nĂ«mak Anutuuk wa ngaĂ¶Ă¶k nimĂ«ak wĂ«Ă«n piiring nĂ«mpenen Ă«a.â
