\v 45 Kimang mĂ« pet irak wal Ă«ak sĂ« pim ruurĂ¶en itaangkĂ«n pit piin yakĂ¶m pan Ă«Ă«n ka uraan
\v 46 epĂ«l mĂ«Ă«a. âAr tol Ă«Ă«nak ka ureim? MorĂ¶ktak wiap sĂ«nganĂ«Ă«n wal Ă«ak Anutuun kimang maĂ«.â
\s1 Yesu kĂ¶Ă¶re tokĂ¶rĂ¶a moresi moulmĂ«a
